    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six engine with individual throttle bodies and Double-VANOS variable valve timing. The mechanical integrity is prioritized, with the critical rear subframe reinforcement already completed and a documented VANOS bulletproofing. It utilizes a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox delivering power to a variable M differential lock. The suspension maintains its factory-spec geometry, offering the precise feedback and 50/50 weight distribution this chassis is renowned for. Recent fluid analysis confirms the S54's internal health, making this a mechanically sound platform for the purist collector.",
