      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between performance and practicality. The exterior finish maintains a high-gloss luster, with only minor, age-appropriate road chips on the front bumper that do not detract from its overall sharp appearance. Inside, you\u2019ll find a meticulously kept cabin featuring supple leather upholstery with minimal bolstering wear and a smoke-free environment. Every electronic component, from the intuitive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is robust; it has benefited from a strict adherence to its service schedule, including a recent fluid flush and a comprehensive multi-point inspection. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the tires possess significant tread depth for the seasons ahead. Complete with a full set of service records and two sets of keys, this car is prepared for immediate, worry-free ownership.",
      "price": 34500.0,
