      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This unit is equipped with the desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a rear-biased M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including structural subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system refresh to ensure timing precision. The chassis remains taut with upgraded Bilstein dampers, and the engine exhibits strong, linear power delivery across the rev range. This is a mechanically robust example that balances raw analog feedback with reliable performance.",
